** Set 8 Pre-Purchase!
------------------------------------------------------------


** Get all the new Dead of Winter expansion cards as soon as they're released!
------------------------------------------------------------
Hello HEXers!

The new Hex TCG PvP expansion Set, Dead of Winter, has just been fully spoiled and is going to be released in the very near future! We’ll soon be trying out wacky new decks or tinkering with our favorite old ones with new Set 8 cards (https://hexprimal.us9.list-manage.com/track/click?u=6f302e8d1bf740c6f329ab571&id=ccd4cc9998&e=a230c85bfc) ! Hex Entertainment continues to out-do itself in terms of art and digital mechanics, and the future of the game looks bright with a slew of new tournaments and influx of players coming from the PS4 release (with other platforms being around the corner).

Once again as we've done for the past 5 Sets, we'll be making all the cards available for pre-purchase for those of you who want to get a leg up on the competition. To get started, head over to the Dead of Winter section (https://hexprimal.us9.list-manage.com/track/click?u=6f302e8d1bf740c6f329ab571&id=e61ae0b0ca&e=a230c85bfc) of our shop, or if you'd like more info on the Pre-Purchase check out our detailed FAQ (https://hexprimal.us9.list-manage.com/track/click?u=6f302e8d1bf740c6f329ab571&id=17895e4109&e=a230c85bfc) .

Thanks for all your support, and see you on the battlefield!

